### Get all tasks
GET http://localhost:5225/api/tasks
Accept: application/json

###

### Get a specific task by ID
GET http://localhost:5225/api/tasks/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new task
POST http://localhost:5225/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Finish final project",
  "description": "Complete the tech trends final",
  "completed": false
}

###

### Update an existing task
PUT http://localhost:5225/api/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "title": "Finish final project (updated)",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "completed": true
}

###

### Delete a task
DELETE http://localhost:5225/api/tasks/1
